Text.string: Hey, Vault Hunter! Need your help!
Man, am I glad to see you! Could use a hand over here!
And awayyyy, it goes! Okay. Wait for it, heheheheh!||Uh. I said, “wait for it!”
Okay... crap. Gonna have to do this the hard way! Shorty? You're gonna have to scurry on down into the tunnel and, uh... shoot her till she booms. Okay?
Doesn't that mean we're gonna have to open up the tunnel? It's full of COV!
I KNOW WHAT I'M DOIN', JUST DO IT! Besides, we can waste a few COV. It's no probs. We got this.
Let's do this, big man.
Ready for a brawl.
I am prepared for a hunt.
Ready to throw down!
All right... here it comes!
Three... two... PUNCH TIME!
Shoot her! Shoot Miss Boom-Bottom in her... bomb-y... boom... BUTT! Bomb... bottom. SHOOT IT!
(death screams from being crushed)

Been setting up a new home base, but the COV been sneaking up on us outta this tunnel. Friggin' hundreds of 'em! So I'm holding them back while Tina collapses the whole damn thing. She's up above working on a plan—go help her out!
Ha-ha, YES! See? I told ya Miss Boom-Bottom got this on pop-and-lockdown, didn't I?
Now, let's finish off the rest of these scrubs!
Hey, uh, guys? The base's been under attack while you were messing around with that tunnel. Thought I could hold them off, but they're gaining ground. Get back here!
Come on, Vault Hunter! Mordy's under attack! Let's go!
It's time to save Boomtown!
“Boomtown”? I thought we were calling it the Fortress.
Pfft! That's dumb as butt. We're calling it Boomtown because I SAID SO.||And because I already made a... sign.
I don't see why you get to just—
La-la-la-la-la, not LISTENING TO YOU! LA-LA-LA-LA-LA, BOOMTOWN, BOOMTOWN, BOOMTOWN!
Hahahaha! You two are so cute when you fight. Now let's go save BOOMTOWN!
Help me fight 'em off, Vault Hunter! We gotta secure our new turf! Show 'em whatcha got!
That should be the last of 'em. Good lookin' out, Vault Hunter. The Fortress is secure for now.
Another successful mission, thanks to MY magnificotacular bombing prowess. You're welcome, everybody.
We smashed 'em good, Vault Hunter! AND took back Boomtown! Hell yeah!
Hell yeah!
Hell yeah!
Mordy, quit copying me!
What? But I thought we were like, doing a thing there, man.
We weren't.
Yeah, Mordy. We weren't.
Vaulty-Vault! We needs your help, girl!
Hey, quick! Brick's in trouble!

My boy, my sweet baby boy Brick-a-brack is stuck down there holdin' this door closed 'cause the COV been sneakin' up on Boomtown outta that tunnel—like, hundreds of 'em. Assholes. And I'm up here tryna help out by blowin' up the whole thing, but Miss Boom-Bottom's badonka-donk got stuck and I can't knock her down so you gotta stomp it!
TINA! Hurry up and collapse the tunnel already! I can't hold them back forever!
I'm WORKIN' ON IT! Damn!
We gotta blow up this damn tunnel, 'cause the COV ain't never gonna stop sneaking up on us through here!
Get WRECKED!
And a boom for YOU! And a boom for YOU!
You get a blat-blat for dat!
That's right, Vaulty Vault! Get them suckaaaas!
As a great machine once said: BOOM TIME!
WE'RE NOT FRIENDS! DIE!
We blasted all the COV, but the BOMB STILL HASN'T EXPLODED! Shoot it! Before more show up!
Hell yeah! You wasted those COV like a true badass!
Yeah! Take 'em down!
Ohhh! Way to slay, girl!
Bust 'em up!
Boomtown.
Boomtown!
Nahhh, we're just kiddin'. You're all right, Bird Man.
EVERYTHING IS UNDER CONTROL, BRICK, OKAY?! I just need a... teensy bit of help, up here. So let's BLOW UP SOME CRAP!

Look, alls we gotta do is collapse the tunnel, and, as with most problems, this one can be solved... ah, with a bomb. But, unfortunately, Miss Boom-Bottom got STUCK. And I can't knock her down, soooo: I'ma need you to stomp it. I'ma need you to STOMP IT GOOD!
